 operators which transmit information from one site to an\nadjacent lattice site. Besides substantiating results from the theory for\nGaussian pulses, numerical simulations show their validity for non-Gaussian\npulses.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Aug 2021 03:45:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-17"}
