 range of parameters that are compatible with theoretical\nand experimental constraints, both from accelerator physics and from\nastrophysics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Aug 2021 11:39:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 26 Dec 2021 14:33:26 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 26 Jan 2022 15:44:59 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 2 Feb 2022 18:40:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-03"}
