better learning effects. Overall,\nthis suggests that bug patterns might be a useful concept to include in the\ncurriculum for teachers in training, while tool-support to recognise these\npatterns is desirable for teachers in practice.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Aug 2021 12:43:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-17"}
