gregation step is also included. Our methodology,\nnamed mi4p, was compared to the state-of-the-art limma workflow implemented in\nthe DAPAR R package, both on simulated and real datasets. We observed a\ntrade-off between sensitivity and specificity, while the overall performance of\nmi4p outperforms DAPAR in terms of F-Score.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Aug 2021 13:40:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-08"}
