 70.4% of the cases, and 354 projects are improved in at least\none metric without making any other metric worse. The refactored programs can\nhelp both novices and their teachers to improve their code.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Aug 2021 14:35:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-17"}
